Data refer to surface water (rivers) only.  The flows for ground water are excluded because they have not been quantified yet.

Annual volumes of the internal surface flows and inflows from neighbouring countries are calculated by the method of GGI. Underground runoff is not taken into account.
The inflow of surface water is calculated as total volume of annual flows within the Shirouzu and Gruszka stations. The inflow of groundwater is not considered.
As annual figures for the inflow of surface and groundwaters are not available, the long-term annual average flow of surface waters from Colombia has been used.
